<L>__{interior early evening house bathroom}
<A>__{in the bathtub, daisy and michael cannot avoid overhearing their parents arguing. in denial, michael blocks his ears with his hands and lies back under the water... back in the bedroom amy seems distrustful of ben, scared of how close he is to the edge. we can see the anger in his eyes...}
<C>__{amy}
<D>__{look at yourself. you're still carrying around so much of that anger.}
<A>__{he catches a glimpse of his reflection in the mirror and of the desperate violence in his eyes... ben steps back.}
