<P>__{(trying to calm down)}
<D>__{i'm sorry, i didn't mean to yell at you... things could be so different between us.}
<C>__{amy}
<D>__{yes i know, but it's up to you ben.}
<C>__{ben}
<D>__{yeah... anyway, i wasn't planning on staying. my shift starts in an hour. i will just kiss them goodbye and then i'm leaving.}
